stack: React 19, Remotion 4, TypeScript

@EXPORTS
index.ts: registerRoot(RemotionRoot) — app entry
Root.tsx: RemotionRoot — registers all 18 <Composition> entries

@VARS_CONSTANTS
FPS: 30 — frame rate for all compositions
W: 1920 — default width (16:9)
H: 1080 — default height (16:9)

@FUNCTIONS
RemotionRoot() → React.FC
  purpose: register compositions + trigger font loading as side-effect
  side-effects: loadMontserrat, loadIBMPlexMono, loadPhosphorFont import

@PROCESSES
boot: index.ts → registerRoot → Root.tsx → font loading → <Composition> × 18

@INTERFACES
Compositions IDs: BrandShowcase | FrameShowcase | TypographyShowcase | IconShowcase | ChapterIntro | IntroAnimation | BarChartDemo | NeuralNetDemo | RAGDemo | TerminalDemo | TopTenDemo | CardsShowcase | CTAShowcase | BackgroundsShowcase | EducationalShowcase | ExplainerVideo | ShortVideo | EP01

@DEPENDENCIES
internal: styles/tokens | components/** | compositions/** | hooks/**
external: remotion, @remotion/google-fonts/{Montserrat,IBMPlexMono}

@STANDARDS
- Montserrat: weights 500-800, subsets latin + latin-ext (Czech)
- IBM Plex Mono: weights 400-500, subsets latin + latin-ext
- ShortVideo = 1080×1920 (9:16); all others = 1920×1080
- EP01 = 38160 frames = 21m12s @ 30fps — production episode
- durationInFrames is explicit per composition

@WARNINGS
- Phosphor font registered via side-effect import (./components/icons/loadPhosphorFont)
